changeSet.author: CloudSoft.User1
changeSet.sql: ALTER TABLE NOMENCLATOR_ATTRIBUTE ADD CONSTRAINT NOMENCLATOR_ATTRIBUTE_COMPLETION_SUGGESTION_NOM_ID_FK FOREIGN KEY ( completion_suggestion_nomenclator_id ) REFERENCES NOMENCLATOR ( ID );

changeSet.sql: ALTER TABLE nomenclator_attribute ADD COLUMN completion_suggestion_nomenclator_attribute_key TEXT;

changeSet.author: CloudSoft.User1
changeSet.sql: UPDATE nomenclator_attribute SET completion_suggestion_nomenclator_id=(select id from nomenclator where code='functii_persoane'), completion_suggestion_nomenclator_attribute_key='attribute1' WHERE nomenclator_id=(select id from nomenclator where code='persoane') and key='attribute8';

changeSet.author: CloudSoft.User1
changeSet.sql: INSERT INTO nomenclator_validation( id, name, nomenclator_id, condition_expression, message, validation_order ) VALUES ( nextval('HIBERNATE_SEQUENCE'), 'persoane.exists_denumire_functie', (select id from nomenclator where code='persoane'), 'nomenclator:existsDenumireFunctiePersoana({attribute8})', 'Functia persoanei nu exista in nomenclatorul de functii.', 1 );
